<main role="main" class="inner cover app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1 class="cover-heading">About Me</h1>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4 ">
        <%= image_tag "jason_mamoa.jpg", width: '100%', alt: "Profile Image" %>

        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                    role="progressbar"
                    aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                    aria-valuemax="100"
                    style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                ></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p class="lead">
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Placeat eius voluptatem debitis laborum asperiores libero nulla eaque est! Aliquid voluptate commodi accusamus inventore provident voluptates quae. Id vitae blanditiis labore quo explicabo laboriosam sed culpa.
        </p>
        <p class="lead">
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Maxime repellendus sapiente illum aperiam quaerat quisquam a aut vel, odit eveniet eligendi praesentium voluptate similique modi aspernatur qui autem dolorem dolore ullam necessitatibus sint quibusdam nesciunt.
        </p>

        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controller="jobHistory"

          >
            Job History
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controller="education"

          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-body">
              Job 1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-body">
              Job 2
            </div>
            <div class="card card-body">
              Job 3
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-body">
              School 1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-body">
              School 2
            </div>
            <div class="card card-body">
              School 3
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
